{"tid":716942,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"夏天開唔開冷氣好","createTime":"2018-06-25T16:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T16:36:36.000Z","uid":157720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"13471a9bfb51e0557809a69b3aa518b0ba4dd522","tid":716942,"uid":157720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:26:57.000Z","msg":"話說樓下個阿伯日日三十度唔開冷氣<br />\n跟住我間房一開冷氣<br />\n佢個天花板就濕晒發霉<br />\n日日上黎屌鳩我唔比我開冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n友善地叫阿伯可以自己用清潔劑抺牆減少霉菌<br />\n順手再送多塊布比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後生仔禁唔挨得學人開冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企人而家力撐阿伯叫我熄冷氣開風扇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24dc6906bee6e7b04a94e30cea051da748f4001","tid":716942,"uid":157720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}